WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.094
Taxi! Taxi!

00:00:02.177 --> 00:00:04.096
I'll give you a lift
as far as Grand Central.

00:00:04.179 --> 00:00:07.015
- No, thanks. I'm gonna wait here.
- You're crazy.

00:00:07.099 --> 00:00:10.060
Because I won't give up?
Maybe I am.

00:00:10.102 --> 00:00:12.688
Let go of him.
Give yourself a chance.

00:00:12.771 --> 00:00:14.356
Good-bye, Wick.

